   * In case you need to use a non standard class for WebSocket.
   *
   * For example when using within NodeJS environment:
   *
   * ```javascript
   *        StompJs = require('../../esm5/');
   *        Stomp = StompJs.Stomp;
   *        Stomp.WebSocketClass = require('websocket').w3cwebsocket;
   * ```
